<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User</title>

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- stylesheet -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all" href="styles/user.css">

    <!-- icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,400,0,0" />

    <link rel="icon" href="./images/ph-logo.ico" />

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

</head>
<body>
    <!-- Top bar containing Logo + search -->
    <div id="nav-logo-search">
        <div id="nav-logo-search-container">
            <div id="logo-container">
                <a href="/" id="logo-anchor"><img src="./images/ph-logo.jpg"/><h1>Yappuccino</h1></a>
            </div>
            <div id="search-container">
                <form>
                    <div id="search-bar">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">Search</span>
                        <input class="search-input" type="search" placeholder="Vibe check">
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom nav containing links -->
        <nav>
            <div id="nav-links">
                <a href="/"><i class="fa fa-home"></i> Home</a>
                <a href="/cafe/browse"><i class="fa fa-search"></i> Caf√©s</a>
                <!-- <a href="#Reviews"><i class="fa fa-coffee"></i> Reviews</a> -->
            </div>
            <div id="button-container">
                <a href="/"><button><i class="fa fa-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></i> Start Yapping</button></a>
                <a href="/logout"><button><i class="fa fa-sign-in"></i> Stop Cooking</button></a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <!-- Main container -->
    <div class="cont">

        <!-- stuff on the left -->
        <div class="left-cont">

            <!-- basic info about user -->
            <div class="user-info">
                <img src="./images/user-pfp/gioCrisB.png" alt="user_pfp" />
                <h2>{{userData.firstName}}  {{userData.lastName}}</h2>
                <h3>Email: {{userData.email}}</h3>
                <hr>
                <p>193 reviews</p>
                <p>41 ratings</p>

                <!-- has all the interaction stuff to the user -->
                <div class="interact-cont">
                    <button>‚úâ Message</button>
                    <button>‚ù§Ô∏é Follow</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- stuff on the right -->
        <div class="right-cont">
            <h2>Stats</h2>
            <br>
            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat-num">
                    <h3>41</h3>
                    <p>Updoots</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-num">
                    <h3>1,540</h3>
                    <p>Photos</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-num">
                    <h3>57</h3>
                    <p>Videos</p>
                </div>
                <div class="last-stat-num">
                    <h3>11</h3>
                    <p>Edits</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- review stuff at the bottom -->
        <div class="review-cont">
            <br>
            <h1 class="h1Review">{{userData.firstName}}'s Reviews</h1>
            <br>
            <div class="reviewContentContainer">
                <div class="reviewPicContainer">
                    <img src="./images/review/cafe_maxims_review-400w.png">
                    <h2>- Gio & Cris B.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="reviewTextContainer">
                    <p class="reviewRating">‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÜ</p>

                    <p class="reviewProper">
                        A good mix of Filipino food and a variety of italian/american food. Their baby back ribs is not that soft compare to other places I‚Äôve been to Manila. 
                        The kare kare is good but also not as tender. The spaghetti is really good since my son really enjoyed it. Their flourless chocolate is divine, 
                        and the mango cheesecake is just ok for my taste. I would recommend this for tourists who wants to enjoy a Filipino delicacy and also have a taste of their
                        favorite italian/american food. By the way, the espresso is awesome, can‚Äôt beat that compare to starbucks.
                    </p>

                    <div class="voteButtonContainer">
                        <h3>Ô∏è‚Äçüî• 0</h3> <button>Updoot</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="myCafeContainer">
        <p>Test Paragraph</p>
        <form action="/profile/postcafe" method="post">
            <label>Cafe Name: </label><input type="text" name="name"/>
            <label>Cafe Description: </label><textarea rows="4" cols="50" name="description"></textarea>

            <input type="submit" value="send it"/>
        </form>
    </div>

<script>
    if (!{{userData.isOwner}}) {
        $('.myCafeContainer').hide()
    } else {
        $('.review-cont').hide()
    }
</script>

</body>
</html>

